    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Story</strong></li></ul>In a certain country, in a certain desert, an unknown pyramid has been newly discovered,.<br>You have wandered into its underground labyrinth.<br>You are lost in the labyrinth, and you are trying to escape from the labyrinth with the help of a lighter and a headlight.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Game System</strong></li></ul>The map and items change randomly each time you play.<br>To escape, the player must move the required number of levers to open the exit door.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unknown Entities</strong></li></ul>Unknown entities lurk in the labyrinth. Try to reach the exit without being discovered by them.<br>Each enemy has different characteristics, so be careful and discern what you are doing.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Keys to Clear</strong></li></ul>In addition to making full use of items, the key to escape is the &quot;treasure&quot; that can be found in the labyrinth.<br>Since possessing these treasures will give you an advantage in escaping, you should actively collect them.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Distribution Guidelines</strong></li></ul>Live video and live streaming of games is welcome. Monetization and super chat are also allowed.<br>Please include the name of the game in the title or hashtag.<br>Please keep your videos within the bounds of common sense. Please refrain from abusive language and slander.",
